2026-05-16T19:49:29.5303988Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5304801Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5305620Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5306453Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5307185Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5318586Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5319524Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5320353Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5321157Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T19:49:29.5321887Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
